{"tid":826904,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一部好睇嘅港產片","createTime":"2018-09-18T14:24:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T07:37:36.000Z","uid":165202,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"2a057a92368e3d9e6ec89831224916a010663b0b","tid":826904,"uid":165202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T14:24:34.000Z","msg":"最近睇返好多八九十年代嘅港產片<br />\n覺得真係好撚神<br />\n以前幾乎每年都會有幾部好賣得嘅戲<br />\n英雄本色、喋血雙雄、倩女幽魂、胭脂扣、天若有情、縱橫四海etc<br />\n仲有一系列嘅賭神賭聖賭俠，古惑仔系列<br />\n太多好睇嘅戲，歡迎一齊吹奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家港產唔係話唔好 (好鍾意警匪/槍戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n但就冇左以前嘅味道，演員嘅感覺都冇以前咁自然<br />\n舊時嘅港產真係一份份寶物黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71ca117b7e3a6a47b992c156357573780912cb21","tid":826904,"uid":165202,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T14:24:50.000Z","msg":"周星馳 賭聖賭俠係最正最有演技<br />\n上海灘之賭聖佢真係好撚好戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n逃學威龍嗰期靚仔到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大話西遊仍然係我心中top10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n紫霞仙子呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbfd6a13a278d05fcf3fd01288787461e045a1fc","tid":826904,"uid":162539,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T14:26:28.000Z","msg":"霸王別姬"},{"pid":"1b30244576ab7cf7c355f1e06f3415ee0e2d6396","tid":826904,"uid":165202,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbfd6a13a278d05fcf3fd01288787461e045a1fc","tid":826904,"uid":162539,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T14:26:28.000Z","msg":"霸王別姬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T14:27:13.000Z","msg":"哥哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94a826acb6b026459c6126ad0355ae5e6aa3466a","tid":826904,"uid":34400,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,